title: Similosodus castaneus
text: Similosodus castaneus is a species of <a href="beetle">beetle</a> in the family <a href="Cerambycidae">Cerambycidae</a>. It was described by <a href="Per%20Olof%20Christopher%20Aurivillius">Per Olof Christopher Aurivillius</a> in 1911, originally under the genus "<a href="Sodus%20%28genus%29">Sodus</a>". It is known from <a href="Borneo">Borneo</a> and <a href="Malaysia">Malaysia</a>.
